{
  "stem": "16887.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sala Hudes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we-- when we got there to the little town, was called Kopeisk, which is a few-- I can't remember exactly how many miles from the main city of Cheliabinsk.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time I was already pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they brought us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they send us to work in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were like six people in a room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they send us to work in the coal mines.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave us cards to rations, you know, for bread, for soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to come up from the-- from the coal mines to eat that soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't work long, long day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My husband did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I stop-- I stopped working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I used to get just bread, not any-- not anything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the few little things that we had, we used to go to the market and sell it and buy bread, buy a few potatoes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we survived there for a few months, and my-- until probably, maybe July, no, [INAUDIBLE] September because my son was born in Cheliabinsk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we decided that is not for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got to the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember we were sitting at the station for about two days, two nights until we got tickets, all of us, all our friends.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we got on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we escaped, came back from Russia, came back to town of Lwow, which used to be Poland, but at that time was occupied by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- Lwow would be close to Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we came back to Lwow, we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we stretched out on the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
